"Extra High Rank Sections":
"A new rank has been added to High Rank Sections in the Retem Region.

Higher level enemies means better rewards, but your Power Level needs to be higher before you can enter."

"In this new rank, you will begin encountering enemies with an \"Equalizer\" attached.

These enemies will greatly boost the defense of nearby enemies, but defeating them will drastically weaken those enemies. Defeating Equalizing Enemies should be your highest priority."
